&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Platform Science is looking for a Senior Software Engineer for their Core Product Development team in Chennai.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be involved in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Full Stack Development using Java and Modern Javascript Framework.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
