&lt;p&gt;At Platform Science, we’re working to connect everything that moves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2015, we are an open IoT platform that partners with innovative fleets, application developers, vehicle manufacturers, and equipment providers in the transportation industry to deliver revolutionary solutions to supply chain professionals across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
