&lt;p&gt;We value thoughtful actions and empathy for others.&amp;nbsp; We approach challenges with resiliency and creativity, while encouraging transparency because, no matter our backgrounds or responsibilities, we are one team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Platform Science is seeking a Software Engineer to join our Video team. In this role, you will maintain and enhance our existing video product, a critical component of our platform. You will directly contribute to the stability, performance, and evolution of a core offering, driving innovation and increasing operational efficiency. Your work will directly impact road safety for our customers, making a difference in their daily operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain our existing Video solutions to ensure our customers have a great experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evolve our Video offering developing new features to attend the global market’s expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply software engineering best practices, guaranteeing the deliverables’ stability, performance and quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively in English (verbal and written)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;API software development with Kotlin / Java and Node.Js or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UI software development with React, Angular or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relational database experience (Postgres, MySQL, etc)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cloud software development (AWS, Azure, GCP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic test automation (Unit and Integration)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Will be considered a plus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Event-Driven systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Infrastructure-as-Code (Terraform or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holistic quality assurance (End-to-End, Performance, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Streaming (Kafka, RabbitMQ)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-relational databases (ElasticSearch, MongoDB, Redis)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serverless computing (Lambda, SQS, Step Functions)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some mobile software development experience (Android)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Platform Science collects your personal information to support its business operations, including for human resources, employment, benefits administration, health and safety, and other business-related purposes as well as to be in legal compliance. You can review further details of such collection and use in our&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.platformscience.com/privacy-notice&quot;&gt; Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt; (link for browser:&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.platformscience.com/privacy-notice&quot;&gt; https://www.platformscience.com/privacy-notice&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
